data.revised_prompt: Create an image depicting the Seattle skyline using swirling, energetic lines and bright, emotive colors typical of Van Gogh's artistic style. The view should feature iconic buildings and landmarks of Seattle, such as the Space Needle and Mount Rainier in the background. Clouds are swirling in the sky in broad, vivid strokes, capturing the painterly aesthetic characteristic of post-impressionist era. The medium used for this is oil paint on canvas giving the image a rich and textured look.
